<br>
44-51 Bloodgill goblins in lake of ill omen. level 35 to 40 have 1300Hp hits for 76 max. 13 spawns, use one shock of spikes and one shock of swords to get full exp. you get 2 almost everytime you pull at the 44 to 46, but just pull with shock of swords, then run to puet and begin focus another shock, so hopfully you will hit him with that to and then he is almost dead. And let pet solo the other, while you try nuke him down with a shock of spikes (earth pet) get about 1 bub a hour at 48 to 49 since i could singel pull almost everytime and a lil slower on the lower levels, still the best exp spot for this level. (need jboots)<br>
